│ the issue you've presented. Here's a breakdown of the problem and the proposed             │
│ solution.\n\n### 1. Understanding the Issue\n\nThe core of the problem lies in an          │
│ incorrect transformation within the `foldShuffleOfBinops` function in `VectorCombine.cpp`. │
│ This function attempts to optimize patterns of the form `shuffle(op(A, B), op(C, D))` into │
│ `op(shuffle(A, C), shuffle(B, D))`. \n\nIn the provided reproducer, the two operations are │
